This was made using python 2.5. I also used the python library beautifulsoup.
To view all slides for a particular webpage, put the url in the beginning of the script where it says url = "PUT URL IN BETWEEN THESE QUOTES"

Examples of sites where View-All-Slides works:

http://www.forbes.com/powerful-people/gallery/

http://www.forbes.com/pictures/ekge45i/do-won-chang

http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2094690_2094691_2094802,00.html

http://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2010/08/the-50-greatest-saturday-morning-cartoons/